org.hibernate.metamodel.model.creation.spi

Interface RuntimeModelDescriptorClassResolver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable, Service

    public interface RuntimeModelDescriptorClassResolver
extends Service
    Given an entity or collection mapping, resolve the appropriate persister class to use.

    The persister class is chosen according to the following rules:

    1. the persister class defined explicitly via annotation or XML
    2. the persister class returned by the installed RuntimeModelDescriptorClassResolver
    3. the default provider as chosen by Hibernate
    See Also:
    RuntimeModelDescriptorFactory
